🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to accept value of n and find sum and average of first n number.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE sum_avg(n INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    i INT;
    s INT := 0;
    avg NUMERIC;
BEGIN
    FOR i IN 1..n LOOP
        s := s + i;
    END LOOP;

    avg := s / n;

    RAISE NOTICE 'Sum = %, Average = %', s, avg;
END;
$$;


